Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.78,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not getting anywhere without the first issue.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.39,0:00:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could get Satoshi and Ibara to help.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, even if we can't solve the mystery,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sooner or later, it'll become a thing of the past.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.39,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thing of the past?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.90,0:00:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Let's ask Fukube and Mayaka to help.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:46.68,0:00:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about what happened to my uncle 45 years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.69,0:00:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me find out.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your uncle, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.88,0:00:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secret of that heroic tale will be solved 45 years later by their juniors, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually been doing some research on that time period.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty curious about this picture too.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.79,0:01:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know the story about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.66,0:01:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe we could even use it for our anthology.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.77,0:01:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should use this as an opportunity to do all the research you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.40,0:01:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, researching the club's history was of utmost importance.
